{"tid":2268201,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"連登仔係咪無聽過咩叫白汁雞皇飯潮文","createTime":"2020-11-02T15:11:02.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-04T05:17:25.000Z","uid":196844,"like":43,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"83d6199ac76707d01e76b43818fca4e170d95795","tid":2268201,"uid":196844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-02T15:11:02.000Z","msg":"是咁的，之前有位飲食台巴打講起白汁雞皇飯潮文，跟住同同事（90後）講開以前d 潮文，以為同周星星9叔同頭d 一樣人人都睇過，點知佢地連聽都未聽過。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n究竟係我老左定點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n利申90後 非打手<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />聽過<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />未聽過<br />\n<br />\n汁：<br />\n係大家樂 我叫左去買個白汁<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2254135\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2254135</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/hMNjBPQ6qSI?t=282\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FhMNjBPQ6qSI%3Ft%3D282&d=tGWxp70K68wBh01xS7f0EgbFtlMfP7wF5OAPhGI7yCY%3D&h=02d262a9\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/hMNjBPQ6qSI?t=282</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/LeFbbTsYi4Q\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FLeFbbTsYi4Q&d=tGWxp70K68wBh01xS7f0EgbFtlMfP7wF5OAPhGI7yCY%3D&h=66190f4b\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/LeFbbTsYi4Q</a><br />\n當然原版幾時睇都咁正"},{"pid":"f0cf328fac12dc146d49288db6bbe2b2f5eae602","tid":2268201,"uid":170271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-02T15:13:44.000Z","msg":"好耐冇睇過<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec32449e7c254ad6e05738959f57be4c758671c7","tid":2268201,"u